item.title: Introduction
item.description: Greeting! Welcome to my portfolio site! I’m Julia Yun. I’m currently a master student studying IT in UTAS (University of Tasmania). I’m graduating in July this year(2021). I am a casual research assistant and academic tutor in UTAS. My research interest covers brain-computer interface, reinforcement learning in autonomous driving. I have a Bachelor Degree of software engineering from Nankai University, China. I was an Android developer for more than 5 years.
